0a%20very%20different%20level.%20He%20came%20for%20the%20trial%20and%20I%20don't%20remember%20who%20the%20bowler%20was%20but%20he%20walked%20across%20stumps%20and%20played%20a%20flick%20behind%20the%20square%2C%20first%20ball%2C%26quot%3B%20Bharucha%20told%20PTI%20during%20an%20interaction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20a%20great%20believer%20in%20first%20instincts.%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20see%20more%20of%20him%20because%20I%20had%20seen%20that%20arrogance%20and%20unimaginable%20confidence%20level%20you%20want%20to%20see%20in%20a%20batter.%26quot%3B%20Bharucha%20then%20went%20on%20to%20play%20a%20significant%20role%20in%20Jaiswal's%20transition%20from%20a%20precocious%2018-year-old%20talent%20to%20a%20player%20of%20international%20class%20as%20he%20became%20the%2017th%20Indian%20batter%20to%20hit%20a%20hundred%20on%20Test%20debut%20on%20Thursday%20in%20West%20Indies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20saying%20that%20it%20takes%20a%20village%20to%20make%20a%20champion.%20There%20are%20many%20people%20who%20have%20contributed%20in%20Yashasvi's%20journey%20so%20far%20and%20I%20just%20happen%20to%20be%20one%20of%20them.%20He%20came%20from%20a%20place%20where%20he%20had%20very%20little.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20certainly%20knows%20where%20he%20comes%20from.%20He's%20very%20clear%20that%20he%20has%20risen%20from%20nothing%20and%20he%20is%20conscious%20of%20what%20he%20is%20doing%20now%20and%20where%20he%20feels%20he%20is%20going%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Bharucha%2C%20who%20played%2017%20first-class%20games%20for%20a%20very%20strong%20Mumbai%20side%20that%20had%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ravi%20Shastri%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F41719-ravishankar-jayadritha-shastri-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERavi%20Shastri%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Sanjay%20Manjrekar%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F41124-sanjay-vijay-manjrekar-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESanjay%20Manjrekar%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Sachin%20Tendulkar%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F14-sachin-tendulkar-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESachin%20Tendulkar%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20training%20at%20Royals%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20make%20it%20to%20the%20next%20level%2C%20sacrifices%20are%20required%20and%20in%20case%20of%20Jaiswal%2C%20it%20was%20about%20living%20in%20isolation%20in%20Maharashtra's%20Talegaon%20village%20where%20Rajasthan%20Royals%20had%20an%20academy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTalegaon%20is%2090%20minutes%20away%20from%20Nagpur.%20The%20idea%20was%20to%20isolate%20him%2C%20so%20when%20he%20goes%20there%2C%20there%20is%20nothing%20but%20practice%20on%20his%20mind.%20Even%20during%20COVID%2C%20he%20was%20living%20there%20and%20practising%20and%20there%20was%20no%20halt%20in%20his%20in%20his%20progress%20even%20during%20that.%26quot%3B%20Bharucha%20revealed%20the%20training%20philosophy%20they%20followed%20at%20the%20Royals%20academy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20had%20a%20very%20clear%20formula.%20Whether%20it's%20300%20cut%20shots%20or%20300%20reverse%20sweeps%20or%20300%20conventional%20sweeps%2C%20we%20will%20not%20stop%20until%20we%20achieve%20a%20certain%20level%20of%20consistency%20with%20that%20particular%20shot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20take%20the%20game%20out%20of%20equation%20from%20our%20training.%20Whether%20you%20play%20a%20Test%20match%20or%20a%20T20%2C%20the%20ball%20will%20fall%20in%20the%20same%20place%20but%20how%20you%20approach%20it%20and%20how%20you%20work%20on%20it%20was%20our%20objective.%20If%20you're%20not%20playing%20the%20cut%20shot%20very%20well%20on%20a%20particular%20day.%20then%20we'll%20focus%20on%20the%20cut%20shot%20only.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20has%20always%20been%20about%20eliminating%20the%20weaknesses.%20He%20didn't%20have%20an%20on-side%20game%20and%20we%20really%20worked%20hard%20on%20that%20aspect%20so%20that%20it%20benefits%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20Bharucha%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Royals%20also%20deployed%20baseball%20mechanics%20in%20developing%20Yashasvis%20power%20game.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20worked%20extensively%20on%20the%20baseball%20mechanics.%20We%20have%20brought%20all%20those%20mechanics%20to%20our%20batsmen%2C%20in%20terms%20of%20how%20they%20strike%20the%20ball.%20He%20(Jaiswal)%20was%20doing%20something%20that%20was%20not%20conducive%20to%20generating%20power%2C%20which%20is%20bending%20of%20the%20elbow%20at%20the%20point%20of%20impact%20with%20the%20ball.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20we%20started%20this%20process%20of%20striking%20the%20ball%20a%20bit%20like%20baseball%20batter%2C%20almost%20two%20years%20ago%20and%20it%20was%20not%20natural%20to%20him.%20Slowly%20he%20got%20the%20hang%20of%20it.%20He%20has%20still%20got%20a%20bent%20elbow%20at%20the%20point%20of%20impact%20but%20certainly%20it%20is%20still%20not%20as%20much%20as%20it%20was%20when%20we%20started.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%2C%20as%20I%20said%2C%20we%20have%20eliminated%20that%20aspect%20and%20hence%20the%20power%20generation%20has%20been%20considerable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20asked%20him%20to%20do%20200%20lobs%20every%20day.%20Lobs%20means%20using%20bats%20and%20balls%20of%20different%20weight%20and%20size%20to%20hit%20every%20ball%20to%20100%20meters.%20It%20is%20not%20easy.%20You%20will%20see%20blisters%20on%20his%20palm.%20He%20has%20endured%20pain%20to%20achieve%20what%20he%20has%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Bharucha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20recollected%20how%20they%20got%20a%20side-arm%20slinging%20throwdown%20expert%20to%20bowl%20him%20at%20155%20click%20to%20counter%20Jofra%20Arche%20during%20IPL.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20soon%20as%20Archer%20was%20picked%20in%20Mumbai%20Indians%2C%20we%20found%20a%20guy%2C%20who%20could%20hurl%20the%20ball%20at%20a%20speed%20of%20155kmph%20with%20a%20sidearm%20throw.%20We%20told%20him%20to%20target%20his%20head%20in%20nets.%20There%20are%20not%20many%20batsmen%20who%20will%20be%20able%20to%20take%20that%20leap%20of%20faith%20facing%20such%20bowling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20when%20we%20are%20willing%20to%20put%20ourselves%20in%20that%20position%20every%20day%20at%20practice%20to%20push%20the%20boundaries%2C%20you%20see%20the%20result%20starts%20coming%20and%20you%20saw%20the%20results%20starts%20coming%20as%20he%20went%20after%20Archer%20in%20this%20year's%20IPL.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BBeing%20vulnerable%20and%20having%20accepted%20failures%20is%20one%20part%20of%20our%20success%20story.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689345360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2F092bktpg_jaiswal_625x300_14_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fwest-indies-vs-india-2023%2Fmaking-of-yashasvi-jaiswal-playing-single-shot-300-times-a-day-100m-power-hitting-and-more-4207893%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Playing%20a%20single%20shot%20300%20times%20a%20day%20in%20an%20isolated%20facility%20in%20Talegaon%2C%20working%20with%20a%20baseball%20coach%20to%20perfect%20the%20power%20game%20and%20painful%20blisters%20on%20his%20palms%20after%20continuous%20hours%20of%20range-hitting%3A%20all%20this%20and%20more%20went%20into%20the%20making%20of%20Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fwest-indies-vs-india-2023%2Fmaking-of-yashasvi-jaiswal-playing-single-shot-300-times-a-day-100m-power-hitting-and-more-4207893%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fwest-indies-vs-india-2023%2Fmaking-of-yashasvi-jaiswal-playing-single-shot-300-times-a-day-100m-power-hitting-and-more-4207893%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fwest-indies-vs-india-2023%2Fmaking-of-yashasvi-jaiswal-playing-single-shot-300-times-a-day-100m-power-hitting-and-more-4207893%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Personal%20Data%20Protection%20Bill%20Will%20'Severely%20Restrict%20Scope%20of%20RTI%20Act'%3A%20Activists%20Write%20to%20MPs%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2F02191508%2FParchment-bg.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Digital%20Personal%20Data%20Protection%20(DPDP)%20Bill%20seeks%20to%20amend%20the%20Right%20to%20Information%20(RTI)%20Act%20by%20%E2%80%9Cseverely%20restricting%20its%20scope%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20seeks%20to%20give%20%E2%80%9Cwide%20discretionary%20powers%E2%80%9D%20to%20the%20Union%20government%20both%20in%20rulemaking%20and%20vis-%C3%A0-vis%20the%20oversight%20body%2C%20said%20National%20Campaign%20for%20Peoples%E2%80%99%20Right%20to%20Information%20(NCPRI)%20in%20a%20letter%20to%20members%20of%20parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NCPRI%20has%20written%20to%20MPs%20highlighting%20concerns%20regarding%20the%20DPDP%20Bill%2C%20which%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20introduced%20in%20the%20upcoming%20monsoon%20session%20of%20parliament.%20The%20upcoming%20session%20is%20set%20to%20commence%20on%20July%2020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20letter%20and%20note%20sent%20to%20MPs%20highlight%20several%20concerns%20regarding%20the%20DPDP%20Bill%20based%20on%20the%20draft%20which%20was%20made%20public%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Electronics%20%26amp%3B%20Information%20Technology%20in%20November%202022%20(the%20draft%20approved%20by%20cabinet%20is%20not%20available%20in%20the%20public%20domain)%2C%20including%20the%20proposed%20changes%20to%20the%20RTI%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20draft%20Digital%20Personal%20Data%20Protection%20Bill%20(DPDP%20Bill)%20proposed%20by%20MeitY%20was%20expected%20to%20develop%20a%20framework%20balancing%20the%20need%20to%20protect%20certain%20kinds%20of%20personal%20data%20with%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20Right%20to%20Information%20Act%2C%202005%2C%20which%20lays%20out%20the%20statutory%20framework%20for%20Indian%20citizens%20to%20access%20information%2C%20including%20personal%20information.%20However%2C%20the%20draft%20Bill%20fails%20to%20safeguard%20and%20harmonise%20the%20two%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20letter%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20proposed%20amendment%20to%20Section%208(1)(j)%20of%20the%20RTI%20Act%20seeks%20to%20exempt%20all%20personal%20information.%20It%20does%20away%20with%20the%20exceptions%20carved%20out%20within%20the%20Section%20based%20on%20which%20even%20personal%20information%20could%20have%20been%20disclosed.%20Currently%2C%20in%20order%20to%20deny%20personal%20information%2C%20at%20least%20one%20of%20the%20following%20grounds%20has%20to%20be%20proven%20%E2%80%93%20information%20sought%20has%20no%20relationship%20to%20any%20public%20activity%2C%20or%20information%20sought%20has%20no%20relationship%20to%20any%20public%20interest%2C%20or%20information%20sought%20would%20cause%20an%20unwarranted%20invasion%20of%20privacy%20and%20PIO%2Fappellate%20authority%20is%20satisfied%20that%20there%20is%20no%20larger%20public%20interest%20that%20justifies%20disclosure%2C%20the%20letter%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20proposed%20blanket%20exemption%20is%20especially%20problematic%20since%20it%20does%20not%20limit%20the%20exemption%20from%20disclosure%20to%20only%20sensitive%20personal%20information%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20letter%20continues%20to%20argue%20that%20the%20proposal%20to%20amend%20the%20RTI%20Act%20through%20the%20Data%20Protection%20Bill%20appears%20to%20have%20been%20drafted%20based%20on%20an%20incorrect%20understanding%20of%20the%20RTI%20law.%20The%20draft%20Bill%20errs%20in%20interpreting%20the%20proviso%20to%20Section%208(1)%2C%20which%20states%20that%20%E2%80%9Cinformation%20which%20cannot%20be%20denied%20to%20the%20Parliament%20or%20a%20State%20Legislature%20shall%20not%20be%20denied%20to%20any%20person%E2%80%9D%2C%20as%20being%20only%20applicable%20to%20Section%208(1)(j)%20and%20not%20to%20the%20whole%20of%20Section%208(1).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20perusal%20of%20the%20original%20gazette%20notification%20of%20the%20RTI%20Act%20shows%20that%20by%20virtue%20of%20its%20placement%20and%20indentation%2C%20it%20is%20applicable%20to%20all%20of%20Section%208(1)%20and%20not%20merely%20Section%208(1)(j).%20There%20are%20several%20judicial%20pronouncements%20to%20this%20effect%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20letter%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20the%20letter%20notes%20that%20it%20is%20well%20established%20that%20access%20to%20granular%20information%2C%20including%20personal%20information%2C%20is%20critical%20to%20empower%20people%20to%20undertake%20collective%20monitoring%20and%20ensure%20they%20are%20able%20to%20access%20their%20rights%20and%20entitlements.%20This%20principle%20is%20well%20recognised%20and%20has%20been%20adopted%20in%20various%20welfare%20programmes%20and%20schemes.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20proposed%20Bill%20will%20potentially%20place%20impediments%20and%20restrictions%20on%20such%20public%20disclosures.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20letter%20has%20been%20endorsed%20by%20prominent%20activists%20Anjali%20Bhardwaj%2C%20Venkatesh%20Nayak%2C%20Nikhil%20Dey%2C%20Rakesh%20Reddy%20Dubbudu%2C%20Pradip%20Pradhan%2C%20Pankti%20Jog%2C%20Dr.%20Shaikh%2C%20Aruna%20Roy%2C%20Shailesh%20Gandhi%2C%20Amrita%20Johri%2C%20Rolly%20Shivhare%2C%20Pradeep%20Raparia%2C%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689345311000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2F02191508%2FParchment-bg.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fpersonal-data-protection-bill-will-severely-restrict-scope-of-rti-act-activists-write-to-mps%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20National%20Campaign%20for%20Peoples'%20Right%20to%20Information%20has%20written%20to%20MPs%20highlighting%20concerns%20regarding%20the%20Digital%20Personal%20Data%20Protection%20Bill%2C%20which%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20introduced%20in%20the