far%20from%20being%20realized.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20still%20at%20the%20iPhone%202G%2C%203G%20point%2C%26quot%3B%20Mostaque%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20next%20year%20is%20the%20take-off.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20Stability%20AI%20chief%20has%20emerged%20as%20one%20of%20the%20more%20speculative%20leaders%20in%20the%20AI%20space%2C%20one%20who%20is%20prone%20to%20making%20zany%20claims%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstability-ai-ceo-employees-going-die-openai-google-meta-report-2023-2%5C%22%3Ehe%20once%20told%20his%20employees%20they%20were%20all%20going%20to%20die%20this%20year%3C%2Fa%3E)%2C%20he's%20not%20wrong%20to%20signal%20just%20how%20much%20further%20there%20is%20to%20go%20on%20AI.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20call%2C%20Michael%20Briest%2C%20head%20of%20European%20technology%20research%20at%20UBS%2C%20suggested%20that%20around%206%25%20of%20earnings%20calls%20this%20year%20have%20made%20mention%20of%20AI%2C%20while%20around%20a%20quarter%20of%20companies%20in%20the%20software%20sector%20have%20done%20so.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20noted%20earlier%20this%20week%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhundreds-of-ceos-talked-about-chatgpt-on-h1-earnings-calls-2023-7%5C%22%3Ecorporate%20America%20definitely%20can't%20help%20itself%20from%20talking%20nonstop%20about%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20ChatGPT%20mentioned%20in%20at%20least%20153%20earnings%20transcripts%20reviewed%20by%20Insider%20in%20the%20first%20six%20months%20of%20the%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20that's%20going%20to%20be%20far%2C%20far%20greater%20if%20Mostaque%20is%20right%3A%20he%20estimates%2050%25%20of%20all%20CEOs%20will%20make%20mention%20of%20AI%20by%20next%20year.%20There%20are%20a%20couple%20of%20different%20reasons%20for%20thinking%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20one%2C%20AI%20has%20primarily%20been%20a%20consumer-level%20spectacle%20so%20far.%20Everything%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchatgpt-openai-web-browsing-plug-change-how-we-use-internet-2023-5%5C%22%3EChatGPT%20plugins%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Microsoft's%20integration%20of%20AI%20into%20Bing%2C%20to%20Google's%20introduction%20of%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-bard-launch-europe-brazil-new-features-languages-2023-7%5C%22%3EAI%20chatbot%20Bard%2C%20%3C%2Fa%3Eas%20well%20as%20Stability%20AI's%20text-to-image%20generator%20have%20all%20revolved%20around%20consumers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20an%20explosion%20waiting%20to%20happen%20once%20AI%20gets%20beyond%20the%20consumer%2C%20according%20to%20Mostaque.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20calm%20before%20the%20storm%20because%20the%20models%20aren't%20quite%20enterprise-ready%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPart%20of%20the%20reason%20for%20this%20is%20that%20because%20companies%20need%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-gpt4-ai-model-got-lazier-dumber-chatgpt-2023-7%5C%22%3Etrain%20AI%20models%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20sensitive%2C%20in-house%20data%2C%20there's%20some%20natural%20wariness%20about%20who%20and%20what%20they're%20exposing%20that%20data%20to.%20Formatting%20data%20to%20be%20useful%20in%20a%20model%20takes%20time%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20once%20that%20realization%20of%20AI%20at%20an%20enterprise%20level%20happens%2C%20it%20won't%20just%20help%20companies%20put%20the%20technology%20to%20good%20use.%20It'll%20spark%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-versus-google-microsoft-startups-chatgpt-competitors-2023-4%5C%22%3E%C2%A0fierce%20competition%20among%20rival%20firms%3C%2Fa%3E%20across%20sectors%20far%20beyond%20Silicon%20Valley%2C%20which%20pushes%20AI%20penetration%20further%20along.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOnce%20your%20competitors%20start%20implementing%20it%2C%20you%20have%20to%20keep%20up%20due%20to%20the%20productivity%20gains%20and%20due%20to%20the%20competitive%20pressure%2C%26quot%3B%20Mostaque%20said%2C%20noting%20that%20it%20won't%20take%20%26quot%3Ba%20huge%20amount%20of%20time%26quot%3B%20for%20companies%20to%20train%20AI%20models%20given%20the%20data%20lakes%20they%20sit%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20just%20need%20to%20have%20the%20right%20models%20in%20the%20right%20way%20to%20enable%20these%20outcomes%20that%20increase%20productivity%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMostaque%20has%20a%20simple%20message%20for%20those%20who%20don't%20embrace%20AI%20wholeheartedly%3A%20%26quot%3BYou'll%20see%20the%20market%20punishing%20those%20that%20don't%20use%20this.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20now%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-hype-could-end-up-like-dot-com-bubble-investor-2023-6%5C%22%3EAI%20bubble%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20still%20rapidly%20expanding.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstability-ai-emad-mostaque-ubs-chatgpt-era-begin-2023-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689343176000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F642db191de7d9200193a277a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstability-ai-emad-mostaque-ubs-chatgpt-era-begin-2023-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Stability%20AI's%20CEO%2C%20Emad%20Mostaque%2C%20said%20during%20a%20roundtable%20discussion%20that%20he%20believed%20the%20real%20force%20of%20AI%20would%20be%20felt%20next%20year.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22hchowdhury%40insider.com%20(Hasan%20Chowdhury)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstability-ai-emad-mostaque-ubs-chatgpt-era-begin-2023-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22JSW%20Energy%20Q1%20results%3A%20Net%20profit%20declines%20over%2048%25%20to%20Rs%20290%20crore%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689343089000%2C%22v