dia-1.jpg%20831w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F14185530%2FVibes-Of-India-Vibes-Of-India-Vibes-Of-India-Vibes-Of-India-1-300x219.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-663223%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22606%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EReceipt%20showing%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20membership%20at%20Alliance%20Francaise%20(AF)%20Ahmedabad.%20Photo%3A%20Vibes%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForler%20and%20Modi%20are%20contemporaries%20and%20became%20friends.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20over%201%2C000%20members%2C%20but%20Narendrabhai%20was%20one%20of%20the%20few%20I%20made%20a%20connection%20with.%20I%20would%20be%20standing%20at%20the%20door%20greeting%20people%20at%20every%20cultural%20event%20and%20I%20remember%20Narendrabhai%20was%20a%20regular.%20One%20time%20he%20came%20to%20my%20office%20asking%20permission%20to%20borrow%20an%20expensive%20coffee%20table%20book%20on%20photography%20from%20the%20library.%20I%20remembered%20that%20and%20later%2C%20when%20the%20famous%20French%20photographer%20Henri%20Cartier-Bresson%20was%20visiting%20Ahmedabad%2C%20I%20invited%20Narendrabhai%20to%20meet%20him%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Forler%2C%20who%20moved%20on%20to%20the%20French%20Embassy%20in%20Delhi%20in%201989%20and%20now%20lives%20in%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F14185759%2FVibes-Of-India-Vibes-Of-India-Vibes-Of-India-Vibes-Of-India.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22831%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F14185759%2FVibes-Of-India-Vibes-Of-India-Vibes-Of-India-Vibes-Of-India.jpg%20831w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F14185759%2FVibes-Of-India-Vibes-Of-India-Vibes-Of-India-Vibes-Of-India-300x219.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-663225%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22606%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EReceipt%20showing%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20membership%20at%20Alliance%20Francaise%20(AF)%20Ahmedabad.%20Photo%3A%20Vibes%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20remained%20a%20member%20of%20AF%20Ahmedabad%20for%20eight%20years%20and%20judging%20by%20his%20speech%20in%20Paris%2C%20he%20has%20happy%20memories.%20Pavan%20Bakeri%2C%20President%20of%20AF%20Ahmedabad%2C%20first%20heard%20of%20the%20connection%20in%202013%2C%20when%20Modi%20was%20the%20chief%20minister%20of%20Gujarat.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20gone%20to%20invite%20him%20to%20a%20concert%20we%20were%20organising%20and%20he%20told%20me%20he%20was%20once%20a%20regular%20member%20of%20AF.%20He%20said%20he%20used%20to%20use%20the%20library%20a%20lot.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Minister%20Modi%20never%20did%20attend%20that%20concert%20and%20AF%20Ahmedabad%2C%20for%20its%20part%2C%20has%20never%20leveraged%20the%20connection%20(though%20it%20did%20dig%20out%20the%20original%20membership%20card%20and%20receipt%20and%20send%20him%20a%20copy%20when%20he%20became%20PM).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVO!%20spoke%20to%20Emmanuel%20Bottiau%2C%20Director%20of%20AF%20Ahmedabad%20as%20he%20was%20waiting%20to%20board%20a%20flight%20to%20Paris%20from%20Delhi%20airport.%20We%20asked%20him%3A%20how%20did%20it%20feel%20to%20hear%20AF%20Ahmedabad%20mentioned%20in%20the%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20speech%20on%20Thursday%3F%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20very%20happy%2C%20of%20course.%20We%20were%20aware%20that%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20was%20a%20member%2C%20but%20we%20never%20publicised%20it.%20AF%20is%20a%20cultural%20association%20and%20we%20are%20not%20allowed%20to%20get%20into%20politics%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFounded%20by%20some%20of%20the%20most%20eminent%20names%20in%20Ahmedabad%20society%2