nutes%20of%20the%20talks%20and%20an%20industry%20source%20who%20attended.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ministry%20%26quot%3Bhighlighted%20concerns%20regarding%20obscene%20and%20vulgar%20content%20on%20OTT%20platforms%2C%20as%20expressed%20by%20Members%20of%20Parliament%2C%20citizen%20groups%2C%20and%20the%20general%20public%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20minutes%2C%20which%20are%20not%20public%20but%20were%20seen%20by%20Reuters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENetflix%20and%20Amazon%20have%20become%20hugely%20popular%20in%20India%2C%20which%20is%20set%20to%20grow%20into%20a%20%247%20billion%20market%20for%20the%20sector%20by%202027%2C%20according%20to%20Media%20Partners%20Asia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETop%20actors%20feature%20in%20online%20material%2C%20some%20of%20which%20has%20faced%20criticism%20from%20lawmakers%20and%20the%20public%20for%20scenes%20deemed%20vulgar%20or%20offensive%20to%20religious%20sentiments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20all%20films%20in%20the%20country%20are%20reviewed%20and%20certified%20by%20a%20government-appointed%20board%2C%20streamed%20content%20is%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficials%20in%20the%20meeting%20asked%20the%20industry%20to%20consider%20an%20independent%20panel%20to%20review%20content%20so%20that%20unsuitable%20material%20can%20be%20weeded%20out%2C%20two%20people%20who%20attended%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20industry%20objected%20but%20the%20officials%20asked%20them%20to%20consider%20the%20idea%2C%20they%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20highlighted%20the%20need%20for%20a%20%26quot%3Bmore%20proactive%20approach%26quot%3B%20to%20ensure%20that%20streaming%20content%2C%20%26quot%3Bincluding%20international%20content%26quot%3B%2C%20aligns%20with%20a%20so-called%20code%20of%20ethics%2C%20the%20minutes%20showed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20code%20already%20mandates%20providers%20to%20exercise%20caution%20on%20content%20that%20could%20incite%20violence%20or%20be%20sensitive%20for%20religious%20reasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20meeting%20was%20attended%20by%20Amazon%2C%20Disney%2C%20Netflix%2C%20Reliance's%20broadcast%20unit%2C%20Viacom18%2C%20and%20Apple%20TV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20companies%20and%20the%20ministry%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'PROPAGATE%20VULGARITY'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20discussions%20signal%20growing%20scrutiny%20of%20India's%20fast-growing%20streaming%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20proposal%20also%20comes%20as%20streaming%20giants%20protest%20a%20government%20order%20to%20add%2050-second%20tobacco%20health%20warnings%20in%20each%20piece%20of%20content%2C%20and%20two%20years%20after%20India%20ordered%20the%20setting%20up%20self-regulatory%20bodies%20for%20complaints%20about%20streaming%20content.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndustry%20executives%20say%20the%20country's%20streaming%20regulations%20are%20among%20the%20world's%20most%20stringent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20an%20April%20event%2C%20when%20the%20government%20agreed%20to%20a%20partnership%20with%20Amazon%20to%20promote%20film%20and%20television%2C%20Information%20and%20Broadcasting%20Minister%20Anurag%20Thakur%20said%20streaming%20platforms%20should%20%26quot%3Bnot%20propagate%20vulgarity%20and%20abuse%20camouflaged%20as%20creative%20expression%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThakur%20has%20said%20complaints%20about%20obscene%20content%20were%20increasing%20and%20the%20government%20was%20willing%20to%20change%20regulations%20if%20need%20be%20to%20address%20the%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficials%20also%20proposed%20at%20the%20meeting%20the%20formation%20of%20an%20expert%20panel%20to%20set%20age%20ratings%2C%20instead%20of%20platforms%20doing%20that%20themselves%2C%20one%20of%20the%20attendees%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20platforms%20said%20they%20would%20ensure%20strong%20parental%20controls%20and%20%26quot%3Bspecial%20care%20would%20be%20taken%20in%20respect%20of%20suitability%20of%20the%20international%20content%26quot%3B%2C%20the%2