%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20account%20that%20reposts%20memes%20and%20other%20viral%20content%20appears%20to%20be%20among%20the%20biggest%20winners%20of%20Twitter's%20new%20creator%20payout%20scheme.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3Binternet%20hall%20of%20fame%26quot%3B%20account%2C%20which%20has%201.9%20million%20followers%20and%20describes%20itself%20as%20highlighting%20the%20%26quot%3Bbest%20of%20the%20internet%2C%26quot%3B%20%C2%A0in%20a%20screenshot%20Thursday%20was%20shown%20to%20have%20been%20paid%20%24107%2C247.00.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20account%20has%20amassed%20its%20vast%20following%20by%20posting%20screenshots%20of%20other%20viral%20posts%2C%20often%20with%20a%20humorous%20comment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%20data-lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%20data-conversation%20data-cards%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%E2%80%94Oliver%20Alexander%20(%40OAlexanderDK)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmims%2Fstatuses%2F1679729076775387142%5C%22%3EJuly%2014%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20makes%20no%20claim%20to%20have%20originated%20its%20content%2C%20a%20mixture%20of%20screengrabbed%20text%2C%20photographs%2C%20and%20videos.%20The%20page's%20bio%20says%20it%20will%20only%20credit%20the%20work's%20actual%20creators%20if%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOliver%20Alexander%2C%20an%20open-source%20intelligence%20analyst%2C%20noted%20in%20a%20tweet%20that%20heavily%20rewarding%20the%20account%20seems%20to%20contradict%20Twitter%20owner%20Elon%20Musk%20saying%20that%20accounts%20predicated%20on%20%26quot%3Btheft%26quot%3B%20would%20be%20demonetized.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHighest%20earning%20account%20does%20nothing%20but%20repost%20other%20people's%20posts%20and%20videos%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Oliver.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20noted%20a%20recent%20post%20Musk%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Banyone%20engaging%20in%20repeated%20theft%20of%20posts%20be%20demonetized.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20was%20replying%20to%20a%20tweet%20w