reliant%2C%20which%20represents%20the%20%26quot%3Bgreatest%20risk%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20UK.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20House%20of%20Commons%20Intelligence%20and%20Security%20Committee%20(ISC)%20said%20in%20a%20wide-ranging%20report%20released%20on%20Thursday%20that%20the%20intelligence%20threat%20posed%20by%20China%20is%20compounded%20by%20a%20%26quot%3Bwhole-of-state%26quot%3B%20approach%20with%20the%20use%20of%20state%20and%20non-state%20players%20for%20spying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina's%20national%20imperative%20continues%20to%20be%20the%20dominance%20and%20governance%20of%20the%20Chinese%20Communist%20Party%20(CCP)%20and%20at%20a%20global%20level%2C%20to%20become%20a%20technological%20and%20economic%20superpower%20on%20which%20other%20countries%20are%20reliant%2C%20which%20represents%20the%20%26quot%3Bgreatest%20risk%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20UK%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20cautioned%20that%20the%20level%20of%20resources%20dedicated%20by%20the%20UK%20to%20tackling%20the%20threat%20posed%20by%20China's%20so-called%20%26quot%3Bwhole-of-state%26quot%3B%20approach%20has%20been%20%26quot%3Bcompletely%20inadequate%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChina%20almost%20certainly%20maintains%20the%20largest%20state%20intelligence%20apparatus%20in%20the%20world%20-%20dwarfing%20the%20UK's%20Intelligence%20Community%20and%20presenting%20a%20challenge%20for%20our%20agencies%20to%20cover%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20a%20result%2C%20our%20agencies'%20work%20has%20to%20be%20targeted%20on%20those%20aspects%20that%20are%20most%20damaging.%20However%2C%20the%20problem%20is%20compounded%20by%20China's%20'whole-of-state'%20approach%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20practice%2C%20this%20means%20that%20Chinese%20state-owned%20and%20non-state-owned%20companies%2C%20as%20well%20as%20academic%20and%20cultural%20establishments%20and%20ordinary%20Chinese%20citizens%2C%20are%20liable%20to%20be%20(willingly%20or%20unwillingly)%20co-opted%20into%20espionage%20and%20interference%20operations%20overseas%3A%20much%20of%20the%20impact%20that%20China%20has%20on%20national%20security%20is%20overt%20-%20through%20its%20economic%20might%2C%20its%20takeovers%20and%20mergers%2C%20its%20interaction%20with%20Academia%20and%20Industry%20-%20as%20opposed%20to%20the%20covert%20activity%20carried%20out%20by%20its%20intelligence%20officers%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ISC%20review%20is%20critical%20of%20the%20UK%20government%20approach%2C%20which%20until%20the%20pandemic%20readily%20accepted%20Chinese%20investments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChina's%20size%2C%20ambition%20and%20capability%20have%20enabled%20it%20to%20successfully%20penetrate%20every%20sector%20of%20the%20UK's%20economy%2C%20and%20-%20until%20the%20Covid-19%20pandemic%20-%20Chinese%20money%20was%20readily%20accepted%20by%20HMG%20%5BHis%20Majesty's%20Government%5D%20with%20few%20questions%20asked%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChina's%20ruthless%20targeting%20is%20not%20just%20economic%3A%20it%20is%20similarly%20aggressive%20in%20its%20interference%20activities%2C%20which%20it%20operates%20to%20advance%20its%20own%20interests%2C%20values%20and%20narrative%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20those%20of%20the%20West%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ISC%20called%20for%20tougher%20action%20in%20the%20government's%20%26quot%3Brobust%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bclear-eyed%26quot%3B%20approach%20to%20China%2C%20as%20it%20found%20that%20external%20experts%20believe%20it%20was%20singularly%20failing%20to%20deploy%20a%20whole-of-government%20approach%20when%20countering%20the%20threat%20from%20China%20-%20%26quot%3Ba%20damning%20appraisal%20indeed%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20Government%20is%20serious%20about%20tackling%20the%20threat%20from%20China%2C%20then%20it%20needs%20to%20ensure%20that%20it%20has%20its%20house%20in%20order%20such%20that%20security%20concerns%20are%20not%20constantly%20trumped%20by%20economic%20interest%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20ISC%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689331920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-07%2F852d1qa_uk-parliament-generic_625x300_15_July_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchina-has-penetrated-every-sector-of-uk-economy-says-parliamentary-panel-4207253%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20panel%20cautioned%20that%20the%20level%20of%20resources%20dedicated%20by%20the%20UK%20to%20tackling%20the%20threat%20posed%20by%20China%20has%20been%20%26quot%3Bcompletely%20inadequate%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchina-has-penetrated-every-sector-of-uk-economy-says-parliamentary-panel-4207253%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchina-has-penetrated-every-sector-of-uk-economy-says-parliamentary-panel-4207253%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchina-has-penetrated-every-sector-of-uk-economy-says-parliamentary-panel-4207253%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%20launches%20space%20mission%20to%20far%20side%20of%20the%20moon%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689331860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F07%2F768x432%2Fskynews-india-space-mission_6218524.jpg%3F20230714120214%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fchandrayaan-3-india-launches-space-mission-to-far-side-of-the-moon-12920892%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20has%20launched%20a%20spacecraft%20to%20the%20far%20side%20of%20the%20moon%20four%20years%20after%20a%20failed%20effort%20to%20land%20a%20rover%20softly%2