t%2C%20on%20April%2023%2C%20Uday%20died%20of%20cardio-pulmonary%20failure%20and%20on%20May%209%2C%20Daksha%2C%20a%20female%20cheetah%2C%20died%20after%20a%20violent%20interaction%20with%20a%20male%20during%20a%20mating%20attempt.%20Two%20cheetah%20cubs%20died%20of%20%26quot%3Bextreme%20weather%20condition%20and%20dehydration%26quot%3B%20on%20May%2025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuraj's%20death%20is%20yet%20another%20blow%20to%20the%20Centre's%20cheetah%20reintroduction%20programme%20launched%20in%20September%20last%20year%2C%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20Centre%20had%20denied%20any%20lapses%20behind%20the%20deaths%20of%20the%20six%20cheetahs.%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20lapse%20behind%20any%20of%20the%20cheetah%20deaths.%20Even%20in%20the%20case%20of%20the%20deaths%20of%20the%20three%20cheetah%20cubs%2C%20global%20wildlife%20literature%20clearly%20mentions%2090%25%20per%20cent%20infant%20mortality%20among%20cheetahs%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20an%20official.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20May%2C%20South%20African%20wildlife%20expert%20Vincent%20van%20der%20Merwe%20had%20predicted%20more%20cheetah%20deaths%20and%20said%20that%20the%20reintroduction%20project%20is%20going%20to%20see%20an%20even%20higher%20mortality%2C%20when%20the%20cheetahs%20would%20try%20to%20establish%20territories%20and%20come%20face%20to%20face%20with%20leopards%20and%20tigers%20at%20the%20park.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689330720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-12%2Fu031k2js_cheetah-kuno_625x300_11_December_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fanother-cheetah-dies-at-kuno-national-park-8th-death-in-4-months-4206891%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20male%20cheetah%20died%20at%20the%20Kuno%20National%20Park%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20today%2C%20making%20it%20the%20eighth%20big%20cat%20casualty%20there%20in%20nearly%20four%20months.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A490%2C%22canonicalUr