zing%20Land%20to%20RSS-Linked%20Trust%20on%20Hold%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F18164526%2FFwBN2HcakAEGvBw.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Karnataka%20government%20under%20chief%20minister%20Siddaramaiah%20has%20put%20the%20grant%20of%2035.33%20acres%20of%20gomala%20land%20to%20the%20RSS-linked%20Janaseva%20Trust%20in%20Bengaluru%20on%20hold.%20Other%20such%20grants%20made%20by%20the%20previous%20BJP%20government%20have%20also%20been%20put%20on%20hold%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Fstate%2Ftop-karnataka-stories%2Fkarnataka-government-puts-gomala-land-grant-to-rss-linked-body-on-hold-1236820.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EDeccan%20Herald%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3C%2Fa%3Ereported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98Gomala%E2%80%99%20refers%20to%20government%20land%20that%20has%20been%20set%20aside%20for%20animal%20grazing.%20This%20particular%20land%20grant%20had%20been%20by%20the%20BJP%20in%20September%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20coming%20to%20power%2C%20Siddaramaiah%20had%20issued%20a%20note%20on%20May%2025%20telling%20authorities%20to%20maintain%20status%20quo%20on%20the%20land%20grants%20made%20by%20the%20BJP%20before%20the%20elections.%20Now%2C%20in%20response%20to%20a%20written%20question%20from%20BJP%20MLA%20S.T.%20Somashekar%20on%20government%20land%20given%20to%20various%20organisations%20in%20the%20Bengaluru%20South%20taluk%2C%20Karnataka%20revenue%20minister%20Krishna%20Byre%20Gowda%20cited%20the%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20note%20and%20said%20that%20the%20allotment%20of%2035.33%20acres%20to%20the%20Janaseva%20Trust%20is%20on%20hold.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20other%20such%20land%20grants%20made%20in%20the%20months%20prior%20to%20the%20assembly%20elections%20are%20also%20reportedly%20on%20hold.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJanaseva%20Trust%20secretary%20Nirmal%20Kumar%20told%20%3Cem%3EDeccan%20Herald%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%