%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Fno-gst-on-replacement-of-parts-during-warranty-period-says-council-123071400450_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Fno-gst-on-replacement-of-parts-during-warranty-period-says-council-123071400450_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Fno-gst-on-replacement-of-parts-during-warranty-period-says-council-123071400450_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22International%20Cricket%20Council%20Says%20Prizes%20for%20Men's%20and%20Women's%20Teams%20Will%20Now%20Be%20Equal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F14134600%2Findian-womens-cricket-team-picture-2022.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20International%20Cricket%20Council%20(ICC)%20on%20Thursday%20(July%2013)%20said%20that%20men%E2%80%99s%20and%20women%E2%80%99s%20teams%20will%20now%20get%20equal%20prizes%20at%20ICC%20events.%20This%20decision%20was%20made%20during%20the%20ICC%20Annual%20Conference%20held%20in%20Durban%2C%20South%20Africa%2C%20and%20is%20part%20of%20the%20Council%E2%80%99s%20plan%20to%20achieve%20pay%20parity%20by%202030.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTeams%20will%20now%20receive%20equal%20prize%20money%20for%20finishing%20in%20similar%20positions%20at%20comparable%20events%20as%20well%20as%20the%20same%20amount%20for%20winning%20a%20match%20at%20those%20events%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.icc-cricket.com%2Fnews%2F3589897%5C%22%3EICC%20website%20stated%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20a%20significant%20moment%20in%20the%20history%20of%20our%20sport%20and%20I%20am%20delighted%20that%20men%E2%80%99s%20and%20women%E2%80%99s%20cricketers%20competing%20at%20ICC%20global%20events%20will%20now%20be%20rewarded%20equally%2C%E2%80%9D%20ICC%20chairman%20Greg%20Barclay%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSince%202017%20we%20have%20increased%20prize%20money%20at%20women%E2%80%99s%20events%20every%20year%20with%20a%20clear%20focus%20on%20reaching%20equal%20prize%20money%20and%20from%20here%20on%20in%2C%20winning%20the%20ICC%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%20will%20carry%20the%20same%20prize%20money%20as%20winning%20the%20ICC%20Men%E2%80%99s%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%20and%20the%20same%20for%20T20%20World%20Cups%20and%20U19s%20too.%20Cricket%20is%20genuinely%20a%20sport%20for%20all%20and%20this%20decision%20from%20the%20ICC%20Board%20reinforces%20that%20and%20enables%20us%20to%20celebrate%20and%20value%20every%20single%20player%E2%80%99s%20contribution%20to%20the%20game%20equally%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20winners%20and%20runners-up%20at%20the%20ICC%20Women%E2%80%99s%20T20%20World%20Cup%202020%20and%202023%20received%20%241%20million%20and%20%24500%2C000%20respectively%2C%20which%20was%20five%20times%20the%20amount%20offered%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689325257000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F14134600%2Findian-womens-cricket-team-picture-2022.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Finternational-cricket-council-says-prizes-for-mens-and-womens-teams-will-now-be-equal%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20decision%20was%20made%20during%20the%20ICC%20Annual%20Conference%20held%20in%20Durban%2C%20South%20Africa%2C%20and%20is%20part%20of%20the%20Council's%20plan%20to%20achieve%20pay%20parity%20by%202030.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Finternational-cricket-council-says-prizes-for-mens-and-womens-teams-will-now-be-equal%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22ITV%20%E2%80%98No%20Longer%20Actively%20Exploring%E2%80%99%20All3Media%20Acquisition%22%2C%22cont