%20industries%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20have%20set%20up%20in%20these%20areas%2C%20with%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fyoutube.com%2Fplaylist%3Flist%3DPL8RbNXSvnr8QmcM6l06yvhPaEhDSc2RL4%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EKapashera%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findiahousingreport.in%2Foutputs%2Fopinion%2Flandlord-tenant-dynamism-in-kapashera-urban-village-delhi%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Elargely%20focused%20on%20textiles%20export%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20while%20Narela%E2%80%99s%20Industrial%20corridor%20specialises%20in%20consumer%20goods%20like%20footwear%20and%20small-scale%20manufacturing%20commodities.%20These%20industrial%20hubs%20in%20the%20early%2090s%20were%20envisioned%20as%20progressive%2C%20manufacturing%20areas%20to%20enable%20the%20movement%20of%20workers%20from%20rural%20to%20urban%20spots%20by%20providing%20employment%20to%20a%20significant%20number%20of%20migrant%20workers.%20However%2C%20the%20social%20geography%20of%20these%20areas%20is%20shaped%20by%20a%20variety%20of%20factors%2C%20including%20social%20structures%20and%20institutional%20barriers%2C%20which%20limit%20migrants%20from%20accessing%20better%20opportunities%20and%20integrating%20into%20the%20broader%20society.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EStudying%20the%20urban%20form%20of%20Kapashera%20and%20Narela%20requires%20an%20understanding%20of%20social%20class%2C%20conceptualised%20by%20urban%20studies.%20The%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmonoskop.org%2Fimages%2Fe%2Fe0%2FPierre_Bourdieu_Distinction_A_Social_Critique_of_the_Judgement_of_Taste_1984.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EBourdieusian%20theory%20of%20social%20class%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20defines%20class%20as%20the%20possession%20of%20economic%2C%20social%2C%20and%20cultural%20capital.%20This%20method%20offers%20fresh%20perspectives%20on%20the%20professionalisation-polarisation%20argument%2C%20which%20looks%20at%20how%20the%20nature%20of%20labour%20is%2