ts-women-education-school%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Einterviews%20at%20Navjyoti%20Foundation%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20an%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fdelhi-bawana-challenges-students-women-education-school%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ENGO%20in%20Narela-Bawana%20area%20that%20provides%20skill%20training%20to%20youth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20coming%20from%20poorer%2C%20impoverished%20neighbourhoods%2C%20we%20found%20that%20most%20of%20them%20were%20hesitant%20in%20taking%20up%20jobs%20in%20Gurgaon%20or%20Noida%20where%20most%20of%20the%20companies%20were%20located.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20commute%20was%20long%20and%20expensive%2C%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findiahousingreport.in%2Foutputs%2Fopinion%2Flandlord-tenant-dynamism-in-kapashera-urban-village-delhi%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eaffordable%20housing%20was%20an%20illusion%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20these%20areas%20which%20are%20made%20for%20the%20upper%20class.%20Dominant%20cultural%20groups%20have%20more%20access%20to%20formal%20education%2C%20cultural%20institutions%2C%20and%20other%20forms%20of%20cultural%20capital%20that%20can%20help%20them%20achieve%20higher%20social%20status.%20This%20further%20perpetuates%20the%20vicious%20cycle%20of%20poverty%20and%20ensures%20the%20status%20quo%20of%20the%20class%20system.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20institutional%20and%20social%20systems%20that%20restrict%20the%20mobility%20and%20prospects%20of%20underprivileged%20people%20in%20Kapashera%20and%20Narela%20are%20complex%20and%20intertwined.%20Addressing%20these%20issues%20requires%20an%20understanding%20of%20how%20economic%2C%20social%2C%20and%20cultural%20factors%20interact%20to%20shape%20social%20class.%20Policies%20and%20interventions%20based%20on%20Bourdieu%E2%80%99s%20perspective%20could%20focus%20on%20increasing%20access%20to%20formal%20education%20and%20cultural%20institutions%2C%20su