death%20globally.%20Johnson%20%26amp%3B%20Johnson%20holds%20the%20patent%20for%20bedaquiline%2C%20which%20has%20shown%20remarkably%20high%20success%20in%20treating%20drug-resistant%20TB.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%2C%20Stop%20TB%20Partnership%20announced%20the%20agreement%20and%20called%20for%20tenders.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.stoptb.org%2Fnews%2Fglobal-drug-facility-update-access-to-bedaquiline%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CFollowing%20lengthy%20negotiations%2C%20Johnson%20%26amp%3B%20Johnson%20has%20granted%20Stop%20TB%20Partnership%E2%80%99s%20Global%20Drug%20Facility%E2%80%99s%20licenses%20that%20enable%20Global%20Drug%20Facility%20(GDF)%20to%20tender%2C%20procure%2C%20and%20supply%20generic%20versions%20of%20SIRTURO%20(bedaquiline)%20for%20the%20majority%20of%20low-and%20middle-income%20countries%2C%20including%20countries%20where%20patents%20remain%20in%20effect.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%E2%80%9Cimportant%20agreement%E2%80%9D%20will%20support%20the%20goal%20of%20ending%20TB%2C%20the%20organisation%20said%20adding%20that%20the%20tender%20for%20bedaquiline%20will%20be%20launched%20by%20end-July.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20patent%20office%20in%20March%20this%20year%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fjohnson-and-johnson-patent-tuberculosis-drug-bedaquiline%5C%22%3Erejected%20a%20petition%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20J%26amp%3BJ%20to%20extend%20its%20primary%20patent%2C%20which%20expires%20this%20month.%20Generic%20manufacturers%20will%20now%20be%20able%20to%20make%20their%20own%20versions%20in%20India%20at%20an%20affordable%20price%20that%20will%20likely%20be%2080%25%20cheaper%20for%20a%20six-month%20course.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJ%26amp%3BJ%20had%20filed%20a%20patent%20for%20the%20fumarate%20salt%20of%20bedaquiline%20in%202008%20to%20extend%20its%20patent%20till%20the%20end%20of%202027.%20The%20move%20was%20part%20of%20a%20strategy%20called%20patent%20evergreening%2C%20through%20which%20companies%20%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eextend%20patent%20rights%20and%20keep%20drug%20prices%20high.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20highest%20TB%20burden%20and%20the%20government%20has%20announced%20an%20ambitious%20plan%20to%20end%20the%20disease%20by%202030%20%E2%80%93%20although%20there%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscience.thewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fmansukh-mandaviya-india-tb-elimination-2025-survey-report-disagrees%2F%5C%22%3Edoubts%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20deadline%20will%20be%20met.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20WHO%20plans%20to%20eliminate%20TB%20by%202030%2C%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Findia-tb-eradication-downslide-who-report%5C%22%3Edelivered%20a%20setback%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20tackling%20the%20disease.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBrenda%20Waning%2C%20the%20chief%20of%20Global%20Drug%20Facility%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fsites%2Fwillskipworth%2F2023%2F07%2F13%2Fjohnson--johnson-letting-nonprofit-distribute-life-saving-generic-tuberculosis-drug-greatly-expanding-access-in-poorer-countries%2F%3Fsh%3D1797a7eb3dcd%5C%22%3Etold%20%3Cem%3EForbes%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20agreement%20gives%20them%20the%20ability%20to%20%E2%80%9Csell%20generic%20versions%20of%20the%20drug%20in%2044%20countries%20%E2%80%94%20including%20Mozambique%2C%20the%20Philippines%20and%20Zambia%E2%80%9D%2C%20countries%20where%20the%20patent%20is%20active.%20In%2052%20countries%2C%20Global%20Drug%20Facility%20already%20sells%20generic%20drugs%20because%20Johnson%20%26amp%3B%20Johnson%E2%80%99s%20patents%20have%20expired%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWaning%20added%20that%20discussions%20have%20already%20taken%20place%20with%20two%20Indian%20manufacturers%20%E2%80%93%20Lupin%20and%20Macleods%20%E2%80%93%20%C2%A0to%20produce%20the%20drug.%20Global%20Drug%20Facility%20will%20accept%20bids%20and%20select%20a%20primary%20and%20secondary%20manufacturer%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EForbes%3C%2Fem%3E%20added%20that%20the%20agreement%20will%20not%20apply%20to%20some%20countries%20in%20eastern%20Europe%20and%20Asia%2C%20where%20J%26amp%3BJ%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpharmstd.com%2Farchivedetails_64_2747.html%5C%22%3Eestablished%3C%2Fa%3E%20an%20exclusive%20agreement%20with%20Russian%20pharmaceutical%20company%20Pharmstandard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJohnson%20%26amp%3B%20Johnson%20charges%20%24272%20(~Rs%2022%2C000)%20for%20the%20total%20six-month%20course%20needed%20to%20treat%20TB%20but%20a%20study%20published%20in%202017%20estimated%20that%20if%20generic%20versions%20of%20bedaquiline%20enter%20the%20market%2C%20the%20price%20would%20fall%20to%20somewhere%20between%20%2448-%24102%20(~Rs%204%2C000%20to%20~Rs%208%2C300).%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689322448000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F08%2F02171246%2FMycobacterium_tuberculosis_Bacteria_the_Cause_of_TB_5149398656.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fbreakthrough-jj-distribute-generic-tb-drug-bedaquiline%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22TB%20causes%201.5%20million%20deaths%20every%20year%2C%20despite%20being%20treatable.%20It%20is%20the%20world's%20deadliest%20infectious%20disease%20and%20among%20the%20top%20causes%20of%20death%20globally.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fbreakthrough-jj-distribute-generic-tb-drug-bedaquiline%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mystery%20over%20three%20'mummified'%20bodies%20found%20in%20Rocky%20Mountains%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689322320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F07%2F768x432%2Fskynews-rocky-mountains-colorado_6218445.jpg%3F20230714103940%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com