0to%20receive%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22It%20Can't%20Be%20Business%20As%20Usual%20for%20the%20State%2C%20'Employers'%20in%20the%20Case%20of%20Gig%20Workers%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Fit-cant-be-business-as-usual-for-the-state-employers-in-the-case-of-gig-workers%5C%22%3EIt%20Can%E2%80%99t%20Be%20Business%20As%20Usual%20for%20the%20State%2C%20%E2%80%98Employers%E2%80%99%20in%20the%20Case%20of%20Gig%20Workers%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubsequently%2C%20in%20an%20email%20sent%20to%20the%20company%E2%80%99s%20top%20management%20marking%20CEO%20Abhiraj%20Singh%20Bahl%2C%20AIGWU%20has%20sought%20the%20company%E2%80%99s%20immediate%20intervention%20to%20resolve%20the%20workers%E2%80%99%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20email%20memorandum%20accessed%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20demanded%20unblocking%20of%20the%20partners%20IDs%2C%20elimination%20of%20multiple%20rating%20systems%2C%20lowering%20the%20minimum%20rating%20threshold%2C%20fixing%20of%20the%20hub%20area%20radius%20where%20partners%20are%20expected%20to%20travel%20for%20jobs%2C%20stopping%20the%20blocking%20of%20IDs%20due%20to%20cancellations%2C%20removal%20of%20automatic%20product%20scanning%20and%20ordering%2C%20one%20day%20off%20work%20for%20partners%20along%2C%20a%20safety%20security%20net%20for%20partners%20and%20taking%20the%20consent%20of%20partners%20before%20bringing%20in%20new%20rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F14131704%2FUC-workers-protest-outside-UC-HQ-in-Gurugram-on-12-July-2.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F14131704%2FUC-workers-protest-outside-UC-HQ-in-Gurugram-on-12-July-2.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F14131704%2FUC-workers-protest-outside-UC-HQ-in-Gurugram-on-12-July-2-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F14131704%2FUC-workers-protest-outside-UC-HQ-in-Gurugram-on-12-July-2-1024x768.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-663139%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EUrban%20Company%20workers%20protest%20outside%20the%20company%20headquarters%20in%20Gurugram%20on%20July%2012.%20Photo%3A%20Special%20arrangement%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPartners%20told%3Cem%3E%20The%20Wire%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethat%20the%20unfair%20mandates%20left%20them%20at%20the%20mercy%20of%20the%20company%20which%20is%20not%20ready%20to%20offer%20any%20redressal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPartners%20said%20that%20new%20rules%20say%20that%20they%20are%20expected%20to%20maintain%20a%20rating%20of%204.7%20to%204.9%20out%20of%205%2C%20which%20is%20based%20on%20customer%20satisfaction.%20They%20are%20also%20required%20to%20keep%20an%20acceptance%20rate%20of%2070-80%25%20(against%2040%25%20earlier)%20of%20the%20total%20100%20jobs%20that%20come%20up%20on%20the%20app%20per%20month.%20Workers%20can%20only%20cancel%20five%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmeena*%2C%2029%2C%20an%20Urban%20Company%20worker%20in%20Ahmedabad%2C%20said%20despite%20having%20a%20rating%20of%204.84%2C%20her%20ID%20was%20blocked%20last%20month%20after%20her%20acceptance%20rate%20dropped%20when%20she%20had%20to%20take%20leave%20for%20her%20father%E2%80%99s%20heart%20surgery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20could%20not%20work%20so%20I%20had%20to%20take%20leave%20and%20my%20acceptance%20rate%20dropped%20to%2040%25.%20In%20addition%2C%20the%20jobs%20that%20would%20come%20would%20be%2015%20km%20away%20%E2%80%93%20outside%20my%20hub%20radius.%20I%20could%20not%20go%20so%20far.%20I%20went%20to%20the%20office%20twice%20and%20told%20them%20about%20my%20father%E2%80%99s%20condition%20and%20why%20I%20had%20to%20take%20leave%20but%20they%20are%20still%20not%20ready%20to%20listen%20to%20me.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCustomers%20can%20cancel%20even%20at%20the%20last%20minute%2C%20but%20if%20we%20cancel%20or%20take%20leave%20for%20genuine%20reasons%2C%20we%20get%20penalised%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPooja*%2C%2026%2C%20a%20partner%20in%20Pune%20said%20that%20her%20ID%20was%20blocked%20when%20her%20response%20rate%20dropped%20after%20she%20took%20leave%20when%20her%20grandmother%20was%20hospitalised%20in%20April.%20%E2%80%9CI%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20parents%2C%20my%20grandmother%20brought%20me%20up.%20How%20could%20I%20not%20take%20care%20of%20her%20when%20she%20was%20in%20the%20ICU%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPooja%20said%20that%20around%20the%20same%20time%2C%20she%20had%20an%20accident%20that%20left%20her%20injured%20and%20made%20it%20difficult%20for%20her%20to%20carry%20the%20spa%20beds%20that%20weigh%20between%2025-27%20kg.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20told%20them%20why%20I%20had%20to%20take%20leave%20because%20of%20my%20grandmother%E2%80%99s%20illness%20and%20then%20her%20death%20and%20my%20accident%2C%20they%20asked%20for%20my%20medical%20records.%20When%20I%20provided%20my%20medical%20records%20they%20asked%20me%20for%20my%20grandmother%E2%80%99s%20death%20certificate.%20I%20was%20promised%20that%20my%20ID%20will%20be%20unblocked%20but%20as%20I%20haven%E2%80%99t%20been%20able%20to%20procure%20my%20grandmother%E2%80%99s%20death%20certificate%20my%20ID%20remains%20blocked.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPooja%20said%20that%20despite%20multiple%20visits%20to%20the%20office%20requesting%20them%20to%20unblock%20her%20ID%2C%20she%20still%20remains%20blocked%20on%20the%20platform%20and%20has%20no%20means%20to%20earn%20an%20income.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeauticians%20are%20also%20required%20to%20pay%20up%20to%20Rs%2050%2C000%20as%20an%20onboarding%20fee%20that%20includes%20a%20kit%20for%20products%20that%20need%20to%20be%20purchased%20from%20Urban%20Company%20itself%20along%20with%20training.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20are%20also%20required%20to%20keep%20purchasing%20products%20from%20the%20company%20which%20are%20sold%20at%20much%20higher%20prices%20than%20the%20market%20rates%2C%20and%20scan%20these%20products%20before%20starting%20a%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENo%20redressal%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMonalisa%20Haldar%2C%20a%20partner%20in%20Kolkata%2C%20said%20that%20the%20products%20keep%20coming%20even%20if%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20place%20an%20order%20and%20then%20they%20are%20required%20to%20pay%20for%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CProducts%20that%20we%20use%20as%20beauticians%20like%20pedicure%20tubs%2C%20waxing%20heating%20machines%20or%20even%20uniforms%20keep%20coming%20even%20if%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20place%20orders.%20Every%203-6%20months%20these%20products%20come%20directly%20to%20our%20house%20and%20the%20money%20is%20deducted%20from%20our%20accounts.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaldar%2C%20who%20is%20affiliated%20with%20CITU%20and%20has%20been%20a%20part%20of%20organising%20workers%2C%20said%20that%20her%20ID%20was%20blocked%20because%20she%20raised%20her%20voice%20against%20the%20company%E2%80%99s%20practices%20and%20helped%20other%20partners%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHigher%20authorities%20have%20started%20blocking%20people%20like%20me%20who%20have%20raised%20their%20voice%20against%20the%20company.%20In%20meetings%20with%20representatives%20I%20had%20told%20them%20that%20new%20rules%20often%20come%20in%20English%20which%20partners%20cannot%20read%20so%20make%20them%20in%20Bengali%20or%20Hindi%20at%20least%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDuring%20the%20pandemic%20in%202021%20I%20visited%20a%20house%20where%20a%20person%20had%20died%20of%20Covid%20in%20the%20very%20room%20in%20which%20I%20gave%20my%20services.%20I%20raised%20this%20with%20the%20company%20that%20the%20partners%20are%20expected%20to%20check%20temperatures%20and%20disclose%20their%20Covid%20status%20and%20not%20the%20customers.%20After%20that%20I%20had%20to%20quarantine%20myself%20for%2014%20days%20and%20they%20called%20me%20and%20said%20that%20since%20you%20are%20not%20on%20the%20platform%20and%20many%20regular%20clients%20are%20looking%20for%20you%2C%20we%20are%20blocking%20your%20ID%20temporarily.%20But%20I%20have%20still%20not%20been%20unblocked%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaldar%20said%20she%20was%20prompted%20on%20the%20app%20to%20pay%20Rs%202%2C000%20to%20get%20her%20ID%20unblocked.%C2%A0%E2%80%9CI%20still%20have%20that%20screenshot%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F14131739%2FUrban-Company-workers-protest-in-Kolkata-on-12-July.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F14131739%2FUrban-Company-workers-protest-in-Kolkata-on-12-July.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F14131739%2FUrban-Company-workers-protest-in-Kolkata-on-12-July-300x188.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F14131739%2FUrban-Company-workers-protest-in-Kolkata-on-12-July-1024x641.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-663140%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22751%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EUrban%20Company%20workers%20protest%20in%20Kolkata%20on%20July%2012.%20Photo%3A%20Special%20arrangement%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPartners%20also%20said%20that%20they%20are%20being%20forced%20to%20sign%20up%20for%20the%20new%20MG%20plan%20upon%20payment%20of%20Rs%202%2C000%20and%20failure%20to%20do%20so%20is%20resulting%20in%20fewer%20jobs.%20The%20MG%20plan%20or%20Minimum%20Guarantee%20Plan%20requires%20workers%20to%20pay%20a%20subscription%20fee%20starting%20from%20Rs%202%2C000%20for%20a%20minimum%20number%20of%20jobs%20that%20will%20be%20provided%20to%20them%20along%20with%20a%20target%20for%20the%20month%20that%20varies%20across%20categories%20like%20Classic%2C%20Prime%20and%20Luxe%20for%20beauty%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Furban-company-sues-workers-for-protesting-against-unfair-labour-practices-protest-called-off%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20workers%20had%20protested%20against%20this%20subscription%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShehnaz*%2C%2035%2C%20a%20housewife%20who%20works%20as%20a%20partner%20in%20Ahmedabad%2C%20said%20that%20since%20she%20refused%20to%20sign%20up%20for%20the%20new%20MG%20plan%2C%20she%20has%20received%20only%20three%20jobs%20this%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20a%20rating%20of%204.9.%20Yet%20I%20am%20getting%20barely%205-6%20jobs%20every%20month%20since%20I%20refused%20to%20sign%20up%20for%20the%20new%20MG%20plan.%20Earlier%20I%20did%20up%20to%2030%20jobs%20a%20month%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20fewer%20jobs%2C%20Shehnaz%20said%20it%20is%20getting%20increasingly%20difficult%20to%20manage%20her%20household%20expenses%20as%20well%20as%20financing%20the%20education%20of%20her%20two%20school%20going%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20written%20to%20Urban%20Company%20for%20a%20statement.%20This%20article%20will%20be%20updated%20if%20and%20when%20a%20response%20is%20received.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENeed%20for%20government%20intervention%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20estimates%20by%20AIGWU%2C%20Urban%20Company%20employs%20more%20than%2045%2C000%20workers%20who%20work%20on%20the%20platform%20in%2057%20Indian%20cities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20also%20has%20offices%20in%2017%20Indian%20cities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20the%20company%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.urbancompany.com%2Fblog%2Furban-company-and-nsdc-enter-into-a-partnership-on-world-youth-skills-day%2F%5C%22%3Esigned%20an%20Memorandum%20of%20Understanding%20(MoU)%20with%20the%20National%20Skill%20Development%20Corporation%20(NSDC)%3C%2Fa%3E%20under%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Skill%20Development%20and%20Entrepreneurship%20and%20became%20a%20strategic%20partner%20for%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20Skill%20India%20Mission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20government%20should%20bring%20a%20proper%20policy%20for%20the%20gig%20workers%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Suman%20Das%20Mahapatra%2C%20Karnataka%20coordinator%20for%20the%20AlGWA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThough%20they%20are%20partners%20and%20are%20supposed%20to%20work%20according%20to%20their%20convenience%2C%20they%20should%20not%20be%20working%20more%20than%208-9%20hours.%20They%20are%20working%20for%20more%20than%2013-14%20hours.%20So%20there%20needs%20to%20be%20a%20policy%20in%20place.%20In%20addition%2C%20there%20should%20be%20an%20employer-employee%20relationship%20so%20that%20they%20get%20legal%20protection%20in%20case%20of%20any%20kind%20of%20exploitation%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mahapatra%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20should%20be%20proper%20vigilance%20and%20redressal%20authority%20who%20will%20listen%20to%20the%20partners%E2%80%99%20grievances%20and%20bring%20the%20management%20and%20partners%20to%20the%20discussion%20table.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShaik%20Salauddin%2C%20national%20general%20secretary%2C%20Indian%20Federation%20of%20App-based%20Transport%20Workers%20(IFAT)%2C%20an%20independent%20organisation%20that%20is%20advocating%20to%20the%20government%20for%20legal%20reforms%20for%20gig%20workers%2C%20said%20that%20government%20intervention%20is%20essential.%20%E2%80%9COur%20focus%20is%20three-fold%3B%20job%20guarantee%2C%20social%20security%2C%20and%20finally%20there%20should%20be%20a%20law%20that%20should%20cover%20gig%20and%20platform%20workers.%20We%20are%20appealing%20to%20the%20governments%20to%20bring%20in%20legal%20changes.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22From%20Health%20and%20Harassment%20to%20Income%20Security%20and%20Loans%2C%20India's%20Gig%20Workers%20Need%20Support%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fcovid-19-lockdown-delivery-gig-workers%5C%22%3EFrom%20Health%20and%20Harassment%20to%20Income%20Security%20and%20Loans%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20Gig%20Workers%20Need%20Support%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESalauddin%20has%20worked%20with%20the%20Rajasthan%20government%20and%20advocated%20for%20a%20law%20for%20gig%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20first%20of%20its%20kind%20legislation%2C%20the%20Rajasthan%20government%20recently%20released%20the%20draft%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.medianama.com%2F2023%2F07%2F223-gig-workers-rajasthan-bill-gig-workers-union-ifat-feedback%2F%5C%22%3ERajasthan%20Platform%20Based%20Gig%20Workers%20(Registration%20and%20Welfare)%20Bill%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20invited%20public%20comments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CGovernment%20intervention%20is%20essential%20because%20they%20(gig%20workers)%20are%20a%20key%20vote%20bank%2C%E2%80%9D%20Salauddin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20NITI%20Ayog%20policy%20brief%20paper%20from%20June%202022%20titled%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.niti.gov.in%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2F2022-06%2FPolicy_Brief_India%2527s_Booming_Gig_and_Platform_Economy_27062022.pdf%5C%22%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20Booming%20Gig%20and%20Economy%20Platform%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20an%20estimated%20that%2077%20lakh%20(7.7%20million)%20workers%20were%20engaged%20in%20the%20gig%20economy%20in%202020-21.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20gig%20workforce%20is%20expected%20to%20expand%20to%202.35%20crore%20(23.5%20million)%20workers%20by%202029-30%2C%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThose%20political%20parties%20who%20are%20not%20thinking%20about%20gig%20workers%20they%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20go%20far.%20In%20upcoming%20elections%2C%20workers%20welfare%20should%20be%20made%20a%20poll%20plank%20because%20workers%20are%20raising%20their%20voice%20and%20they%20are%20demanding%20job%20guarantees%20and%20benefits%2C%E2%80%9D%20Salauddin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20appealing%20to%20state%20governments%20hoping%20for%20change.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20while%20the%20Union%20government%20notified%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fvvgnli.gov.in%2Fen%2Fcode-social-security-2020%5C%22%3ESocial%20Security%20Code%2C%202020%2C%20%3C%2Fa%3Eit%20still%20has%20not%20been%20implemented.%C2%A0%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20been%20three%20years%2C%20why%20isn%E2%80%99t%20it%20being%20implemented%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSince%20it%20is%20not%20happening%20at%20the%20central%20level%20yet%2C%20we%20are%20continuing%20our%20advocacy%20in%20states%20and%20even%20tier%201%20and%20tier%202%20cities%20to%20give%20rights%20to%20gig%20workers.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E*Names%20changed%20to%20protect%20workers%E2%80%99%20identities.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689322155000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F14131544%2FUC-workers-protest-outside-UC-HQ-in-Gurugram-on-12-July.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Furban-company-workers-protest-job-losses-after-blocked-ids-unrealistic-rating-requirements%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22On%20July%2012%2C%20partners%20across%20Indian%20cities%20including%20Delhi%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20Bengaluru%2C%20Kolkata%20and%20Hyderabad%20held%20a%20nationwide%20protest%20aided%20by%20All%20India%20Gig%20Workers%20Union%20against%20arbitrary%20blocking%20of%20IDs%20and%20new%20rules%20that%20have%20led%20them%20t