less%20than%20six%20months%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EEconomic%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Feconomy%2Findicators%2F21-unorganised-workers-exit-pm-pension-scheme%2Farticleshow%2F101737850.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20total%20subscribers%20under%20the%20scheme%20fell%20to%204.43%20million%20on%20July%2011%2C%20down%201.19%20million%20from%205.62%20million%20on%20January%2031%2C%20as%20per%20government%20data.%20This%20has%20raised%20questions%20about%20the%20viability%20of%20the%20scheme%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EEconomic%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20experts%2C%20high%20inflation%20and%20rising%20cost%20of%20living%20has%20increased%20the%20workers%E2%80%99%20difficulties%20and%20could%20be%20preventing%20them%20from%20contributing%20to%20the%20voluntary%20pension%20scheme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CStubbornly%20high%20prices%20have%20raised%20the%20actual%20cost%20of%20living%2C%20making%20it%20difficult%20for%20these%20workers%20to%20sustain%20the%20burden%20of%20monthly%20contribution%20under%20the%20scheme%2C%E2%80%9D%20labour%20economist%20K.R.%20Shyam%20Sundar%20told%20the%20%3Cem%3EEconomic%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20would%20not%20be%20surprising%20if%20these%20are%20permanent%20exits%2C%20with%20workers%20actually%20withdrawing%20their%20contribution%20along%20with%20the%20interest%20earned%20on%20it%20as%20high%20prices%20continue%20to%20pinch%20on%20their%20pockets%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sundar%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20scheme%20guidelines%20state%20that%20a%20subscriber%20will%20be%20allowed%20to%20withdraw%20their%20share%20of%20contribution%20with%20savings%20bank%20interest%20rate%20if%20they%20exit%20the%20scheme%20in%20less%20than%2010%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20if%20a%20subscriber%20exits%20after%2010%20years%20or%20more%20but%20before%20superannuation%20at%20the%20age%20of%2060%20years%2C%20the%20beneficiary%E2%80%99s%20share%20of%20contribution%20along%20with%20accumulated%20interest%20as%20actually%20earned%20by%20the%20fund%20or%20at%20the%20savings%20bank%20interest%20rate%2C%20whichever%20is%20higher%2C%20will%20be%20credited%20to%20the%20beneficiary%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20scheme%2C%20launched%20with%20the%20aim%20of%20extending%20social%20security%20benefits%20to%20unorganised%20workers%2C%20caters%20to%20those%20in%20the%2018-40%20age%20group%20and%20earn%20less%20than%20Rs%2015%2C000%20per%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689321202000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F14115201%2FFemale_construction_worker_in_India_4180249684.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2F21-informal-workers-leave-pm-pension-scheme-inflation-cost-of-living-main-factors%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20total%20subscribers%20under%20the%20scheme%20fell%20to%204.43%20million%20on%20July%2011%2C%20down%201.19%20million%20from%205.62%20million%20on%20January%2031.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2F21-informal-workers-leave-pm-pension-scheme-inflation-cost-of-living-main-factors%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Priyanka%20chats%20with%20Idris%20Elba%2C%20John%20Cena%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689321159000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-101751403%2Cimgsize-18616.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fsee-video-priyanka-chopra-caught-in-an-animated-discussion-with-idris-elba-john-cena-on-heads-of-state-set%2Farticleshow%2F101751437.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F101751437.cms%5C%22%20hspac