%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F298376%2Fmolbio-diagnostics-truenat-covid-testing-raises-funding%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20COVID-19%20pandemic%3C%2Fa%3E%20hit%2C%20the%20world%20slowed%20to%20a%20halt%2C%20and%20the%20profound%20impact%20of%20the%20pandemic%20was%20mixed%20somewhere%20with%20a%20period%20of%20deep%20reflection%20and%20changes.%20For%20those%20of%20us%20who%20could%20be%20safe%20in%20our%20homes%2C%20hobbies%20like%20gardening%20and%20cooking%20flourished%2C%20and%20many%20people%20found%20new%20avenues%20to%20explore.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilar%20was%20the%20story%20of%20Udaipur-based%20Digvijay%20Singh%2C%20then%2016.%20He%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20free%20time%20in%20hand%20with%20school%20being%20online.%20I%20wanted%20to%20invest%20my%20energy%20into%20something%20interesting%20and%20fun.%20After%20various%20tries%2C%20I%20found%20myself%20making%20chocolates%20at%20home.%20This%20was%20the%20start%20of%20my%20brand%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDigvijay%20is%2019%20today%2C%20and%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F201233%2Fhow-to-make-vegan-glutenfree-dark-chocolate-weekend-workshop-diy-nitin-chordia-chennai-lifestyle%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eself-taught%20chocolatier%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewho%20runs%20Saraam%2C%20under%20the%20ambit%20of%20which%20he%20has%20sold%20over%20two%20tonnes%20of%20chocolates%20to%20hundreds%20of%20happy%20customers%20across%20the%20country%20including%20Delhi%2C%20Bengaluru%2C%20Udaipur%2C%20and%20Jaipur.%20What%E2%80%99s%20interesting%20about%20Digvijay%E2%80%99s%20endeavour%20is%20that%20he%20incorporates%20indigenous%20fruits%20and%20spices%20like%20%3Cem%3Ebaer%2C%20jamun%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Esaffron%2C%20and%20more%20to%20put%20India%E2%80%99s%20botanical%20heritage%20and%20biodiversity%20on%20the%20culinary%20map.%3C%2F