%20is%20enough%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20social%20divide%20of%20our%20country%20became%20so%20much%20more%20visible.%20I%20started%20to%20ponder%20if%20I%20could%20be%20of%20some%20help%20and%20if%20I%20could%20use%20my%20resources%20to%20make%20things%20better%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20birth%20of%20Aazol%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApurva%20decided%20to%20take%20early%20retirement%20in%202021%20to%20brainstorm%20ideas.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20spoke%20to%20my%20son%2C%20I%20realised%20that%20he%20is%20also%20passionate%20about%20helping%20the%20bottom%20tier%20of%20society.%20This%20was%20it%3B%20we%20both%20made%20up%20our%20minds%20to%20find%20a%20way%20of%20helping%20the%20underprivileged%20by%20giving%20them%20a%20livelihood%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20same%20year%2C%20Apurva%20and%20Siddharth%20went%20to%20Mahalaxmi%20Saras%20Exhibition%20which%20happens%20every%20year%20in%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20exhibition%20is%20by%20people%20from%20all%20across%20Maharashtra%20from%20various%20SHGs%20showcasing%20and%20selling%20their%20produce.%20While%20chatting%20with%20these%20women%2C%20I%20realised%20how%20they%20did%20not%20have%20many%20avenues%20to%20sell%20these%20products.%20There%20were%20so%20many%20snacks%20and%20products%20like%20chutney%2C%20sauces%20and%20syrups%20that%20I%20had%20never%20seen%20before%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHaving%20lived%20in%20Maharashtra%20my%20whole%20life%20I%20was%20shocked%20to%20see%20so%20many%20snacks%20that%20nobody%20knew%20about.%20Additionally%2C%20all%20these%20were%20handmade%20and%20without%20preservatives.%20Those%20women%20also%20told%20me%20how%20they%20do%20not%20have%20much%20employment%20and%20were%20constantly%20under%20financial%20stress%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20conversations%20with%20the%20women%20gave%20the%20duo%20the%20idea%20of%20starting%20a%20company%20that%20could%20bridge%20this%20gap.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20thought%20%E2%80%98Why%20don%E2%80%99t%20we%20create%20a%20marketplace%20and%20supply%20chain%20for%20these%20women%3F%E2%80%99%20and%20then%20in%20September%202021%2C%20Aazol%20was%20born%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Faazol-5-1688737718.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22women%20from%20remote%20village%20in%20Maharashtra%20working%20for%20Aazol%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Faazol-5-1688737718.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Faazol-5-1688737718-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Faazol-5-1688737718-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Faazol-5-1688737718-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Faazol-5-1688737718-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-323132%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EApurva%20left%20her%20three%20decades%20of%20corporate%20career%20to%20work%20in%20the%20social%20sector%3B%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Apurva%20Purohit%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMaking%20rare%20foods%20available%20to%20the%20world%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mother-son%20team%20went%20to%20various%20remote%20villages%20in%20search%20of%20authentic%20food%20made%20by%20the%20locals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20son%20even%20visited%20Naxalite%20villages%20to%20get%20their%20authentic%20snacks%20and%20bring%20them%20to%20the%20world%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20%E2%80%9CFor%20instance%2C%20the%20tribal%20women%20in%20some%20villages%20make%20mahua%3Cem%3E%20ladoos%3C%2Fem%3E%20which%20are%20made%20using%20mahua%20flower%20and%20jaggery.%20It%20is%20endemic%20to%20the%20region%20and%20is%20not%20well%20known%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAazol%20has%20been%20in%20corporation%20with%2017%20SHGs%20from%20various%20districts%20of%20Maharashtra%20including%20Nandurbar%2C%20Wardha%20etc.%20Each%20of%20these%20self-help%20groups%20employs%2020%20to%20200%20women%20every%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20acts%20as%20an%20intermediary%20between%20the%20end%20consumers%20and%20women%20in%20the%20village%20who%20make%20these%20products%20for%20them.%20Its%20wide%20range%20of%20Maharashtrian%20snacks%20includes%20various%20types%20of%20chutneys%2C%20indigenous%20rice%20like%20%3Cem%3EIndrayani%20%3C%2Fem%3Erice%2C%20spices%2C%20%3Cem%3Epapads%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3Eladoos%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20the%20products%20are%20handmade%20or%20locally%20grown%20or%20made%20using%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F283463%2Fmother-daughter-natural-ghee-brand-bilona-nei-native-woman-entrepreneur%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etraditional%20recipes%3C%2Fa%3E.%20They%20are%20also%20fresh%20and%20preservative%20free%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Apurva.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20also%20ensure%20that%20all%20the%20women%20are%20paid%20upfront%20within%2015%20days%20of%20the%20delivery.%20We%20do%20not%20wait%20for%20the%20sale%20to%20happen%20to%20pay%20them.%20These%20women%20work%20very%20hard%2C%20and%20I%20just%20want%20to%20ensure%20that%20they%20get%20their%20fair%20share%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharda%20Gajanan%20Thakur%20(47)%20who%20has%20been%20working%20with%20them%20for%20two%20years%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20my%20village%20in%20Wardha%20district%2C%20there%20are%20no%20other%20work%20opportunities%20other%20than%20working%20in%20the%20fields.%20Women%20are%20mostly%20bound%20to%20stay%20at%20home.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F311837%2Fengineer-quit-us-job-to-launch-villa-mart-mobile-mandi-farmer-suicides-fair-income%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFarmers%20committing%20suicide%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20very%20common%20here.%20When%20I%20started%20working%20with%20SHG%20and%20Aazol%2C%20I%20could%20not%20believe%20that%20something%20like%20this%20was%20possible.%20Many%20women%20from%20my%20village%20joined%20too.%20I%20get%20paid%20regularly%20and%20my%20household%E2%80%99s%20income%20has%20now%20reached%20Rs%2035%2C000%20a%20month.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20840px)%20100vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Faazol-1-1688737277.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Apurva%20and%20Siddharth%20Purohit%2C%20co-founders%20of%20Aazol.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Faazol-1-1688737277.jpg%20840w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Faazol-1-1688737277-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Faazol-1-1688737277-500x261.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Faazol-1-1688737277-768x401.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Faazol-1-1688737277-150x78.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-323123%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22439%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EApurva%20and%20Siddharth%20Purohit%2C%20co-founders%20of%20Aazol%3B%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Apurva%20Purohit%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20only%20a%20year%20and%20a%20half%20in%20business%2C%20the%20company%20has%20been%20able%20to%20cater%20to%20hundreds%20of%20customers%20in%20Maharastra%20and%20around%20the%20country.%20Their%20products%20are%20priced%20in%20the%20range%20of%20Rs%20150%20to%20Rs%20800%20and%20are%20available%20to%20buy%20on%20their%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faazol.in%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewebsite%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20on%20aggregators%20like%20ONDC%2C%20Amazon%2C%20and%20Flipkart.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReflecting%20on%20their%20journey%2C%20Apurva%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20decided%20to%20switch%20from%20a%20well-established%20career%20to%20a%20startup%2C%20where%20I%20did%20not%20even%20have%20an%20office%2C%20was%20a%20huge%20step%20for%20me.%20I%20was%20scared%2C%20but%20in%20my%20heart%2C%20I%20knew%20that%20this%20was%20my%20calling.%20I%20recognise%20the%20privilege%20I%20had%20in%20getting%20an%20opportunity%20to%20get%20a%20good%20education%2C%20but%20many%20do%20not%20get%20that.%20I%20just%20wanted%20to%20give%20back%20to%20society%20when%20I%20still%20have%20the%20energy%20and%20calibre%20to%20do%20so.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1688999464000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Faazol-3-1688737533.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D323084%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mumbai's%20Apurva%20and%20Siddharth%20Purohit%20started%20Aazol%2C%20a%20company%20that%20sells%20authentic%20Maharashtrian%20snacks%20to%20help%20rural%20women%20gain%20financial%20independence%2C%20while%20introducing%20urban%20India%20to%20lesser-known%20food%20items.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A101%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F323084%2Fmumbai-mother-son-duo-start-aazol-maharastrian-traditional-snacks-